config CURL
	bool
	prompt "Compile cURL"
   help
     cURL groks URLs
     Curl is a command line tool for transferring files with URL syntax, supporting FTP, 
     FTPS, HTTP, HTTPS, GOPHER, TELNET, DICT, FILE and LDAP. Curl supports HTTPS 
     certificates, HTTP POST, HTTP PUT, FTP uploading, kerberos, HTTP form based 
     upload, proxies, cookies, user+password authentication, file transfer resume, 
     http proxy tunneling and a busload of other useful tricks.
     
     See http://curl.haxx.sr/ for details.

